from similar but unrelated hedge types.

</para><para depth="0">We could have:
   president isa manager isa employee isa person
  vice-president isa manager isa employee isa person

</para><para depth="0">and hedge types:
company-bowling-team -&gt; (employee+)
5-year-plan-strategists -&gt; (president, vice-president*)

</para><para depth="0">Yes, the president and vice-presidents could form a bowling team,
but it's unlikely that the author of these types had that in mind.

</para><para depth="0">Jeff

